Title: Check Forgotten Password link

Steps:
1. Open https://account.next.ua/en/Login page
2. Enter "auto@test.com" to 'Email Address' input field
3. Click on 'Forgotten Password' link
4. Click on 'edit' link

Expected results:
3. Modal window is displayed with:
- 'FORGOTTEN YOUR PASSWORD?' header
- 'An email will be sent to the email address below with instructions on how to reset your password.' body
- 'Close' button
- 'Reset' button
- "auto@test.com" is inputted in 'EmailOrAccountNumber' field
- 'edit' link
4. 'edit' link is not displayed.
"auto@test.com" is not displayed in 'EmailOrAccountNumber' field.
'Email Address or Customer Number' placeholder is displayed in 'EmailOrAccountNumber' field.